text: Happenings is an album by jazz vibraphonist Bobby Hutcherson, released in 1967 on the Blue Note label. The album features six compositions by Hutcherson, and one by Herbie Hancock, "Maiden Voyage". ==Track listing== All compositions by Bobby Hutcherson except as noted # "Aquarian Moon" - 7:45 # "Bouquet" - 8:10 # "Rojo" - 6:03 # "Maiden Voyage" (Hancock) - 5:49 # "Head Start" - 5:16 # "When You Are Near" - 3:51 # "The Omen" - 6:59 ==Personnel== *Bobby Hutcherson - vibraphone (tracks 1-6), marimba, drums (track 7 only) *Herbie Hancock - piano, box full of rocks (track 7 only) *Bob Cranshaw - bass *Joe Chambers - drums, marimba (track 7 only), triangle (track 2 only), timpani (track 7 only) == References == Category:1967 albums Category:Blue Note Records albums Category:Bobby Hutcherson albums Category:Post-bop albums Category:Albums produced by Alfred Lion Category:Albums recorded at Van Gelder Studio
